data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in Poinciana, Florida! This 4/2 oasis is not just a home; it's a vacation waiting to happen. Dive into the sparkling pool – fresher than your morning coffee. The roof? As young as your last Instagram post – only 4 years old! Step inside on floors so new, they still have that showroom shine.But wait, there's more! The pool heater is hotter than your favorite gossip, and the A/C unit? Cooler than the other side of the pillow – and it's only 3 years old! This place is the Goldilocks of comfort.  And here's the twist – this paradise isn't just for you; it moonlights as a short and long-term rental. You'll be the host with the most, offering a stay so good they'll forget to check out.
